OL,3,CHow dust, the angle of the sun and
OL,4,Cdrier air create more spectacular
OL,5,Csunsets
OL,7,Fand sunrises in winter are, arguably,
OL,8,Fthe finest in the year.
OL,10,FThe cooler temperatures mean that the
OL,11,Fair holds less moisture - and that
OL,12,Fdrier air results in bolder looking
OL,13,Fcolours.
OL,15,FDuring winter, the sun sets on more of
OL,16,Fan angle which increases the amount of
OL,17,Fthe time it takes to set. This allows
OL,18,Ffor a longer sunset.
