OL,3,CHow dust, the angle of the sun and
OL,4,Cdrier air create more spectacular
OL,5,Csunsets
OL,7,FThe angle of the sun also means the
OL,8,Fsunlight has to pass through more
OL,9,Fatmosphere, which in turn means that
OL,10,Fwe see longer wavelength colours:
OL,11,Forange pink and red.
OL,13,FWhy are sunsets so spectacular at the
OL,14,Fmoment?
OL,16,FA few times a year, big dust storms in
OL,17,Fthe Sahara coincide with southerly
OL,18,Fwind patterns which blow the dust
OL,19,Fparticles as far north as the UK.
